_sText:
This map was created over the course of about three hours.  I decided to take a break from making fy_ maps and create something totally new.  On this defuser-explosive map, the field is very open for easy killing, making the rounds very quick and the pace very fast.  Although that is not a typical characteristic of de_ maps, I found this map to be very fun with few players on each team, even though there is room for many players on both sides.

Special Thanks to chizbone for the .nav.
